WEBVTT

00:10.271 --> 00:11.150
Your Grace.

00:11.151 --> 00:13.221
Eunuch Wang, how is His Majesty?

00:13.771 --> 00:14.911
Please come inside.

00:20.171 --> 00:21.701
Meisun...

00:23.051 --> 00:26.421
His Majesty is sinking fast.

00:38.961 --> 00:40.581
What is this item doing here?

00:41.491 --> 00:43.831
Official Ji must have left it

00:43.851 --> 00:46.111
when he visited His Majesty.

00:54.111 --> 00:56.491
I want to teach you
the 13 Acupuncture Spots of the Demons.

00:56.601 --> 00:58.901
There's a point
on the tongue called Haiquan.

00:59.031 --> 01:01.280
Administering a needle here
can have miraculous effects

01:01.281 --> 01:02.600
on those on the brink of death

01:02.601 --> 01:04.341
from a severe collapse.

01:06.811 --> 01:07.981
Ji Yong

01:08.121 --> 01:09.671
is always playing tricks

01:09.761 --> 01:11.701
and never speaks clearly.

01:12.451 --> 01:15.701
It turns out what he taught me
was meant for today.

01:16.651 --> 01:18.391
So everything is part of his master plan

01:19.011 --> 01:20.621
to root out traitors and restore order.

01:21.201 --> 01:23.681
He was appointed as the Administrator
of Lord Qing's Residence

01:24.001 --> 01:25.391
and appeared to have turned against us.

01:25.401 --> 01:27.261
But it was actually
under His Majesty's orders.

01:29.841 --> 01:31.831
When investigating the case in Futing,

01:32.321 --> 01:33.471
His Majesty already knew

01:33.731 --> 01:35.141
that the Duke of Ding's death

01:35.481 --> 01:37.240
was Lord Qing's doing.

01:37.241 --> 01:39.031
So, he can only

01:39.201 --> 01:40.781
let Lord Qing commit treason

01:40.961 --> 01:44.170
to lure all the hidden conspirators

01:44.171 --> 01:45.530
to reveal themselves one by one

01:45.531 --> 01:46.781
and be eradicated in one stroke.

01:49.041 --> 01:50.831
Ji Yong deceived everyone,

01:51.481 --> 01:53.341
even Song Mo and me.

01:53.601 --> 01:57.031
However, the number
of court officials supporting Lord Qing

01:57.481 --> 02:00.311
was greater
than His Majesty had anticipated.

02:00.371 --> 02:02.111
Some princes even

02:02.171 --> 02:04.320
openly sided with Lord Qing.

02:04.321 --> 02:06.231
The one truly commanding

02:06.481 --> 02:07.951
the entire scheme

02:08.401 --> 02:10.341
was actually the one closest
to His Majesty,

02:10.891 --> 02:13.101
leading us to today's dead end.

02:14.361 --> 02:15.621
It might not be a dead end.

02:16.891 --> 02:18.010
Eunuch Wang,

02:18.011 --> 02:19.941
help me lift His Majesty.

03:47.551 --> 03:51.790
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:51.791 --> 03:55.051
=Episode 34=

03:56.801 --> 03:58.501
Maintain the Yuanyang Formation!

03:58.731 --> 04:00.661
Prepare to break through the siege!

04:04.481 --> 04:05.941
They're at their limit.

04:06.041 --> 04:07.181
Charge!

04:12.851 --> 04:14.341
Leave none alive!

04:14.641 --> 04:15.781
Kill them all!

05:11.391 --> 05:15.251
(Qianqing Palace)

05:19.451 --> 05:21.231
Here comes my reinforcement.

05:23.571 --> 05:24.711
Your Highness.

05:26.521 --> 05:29.191
You have been deceived by traitors

05:29.961 --> 05:32.621
and raised an unjust rebellion.

05:33.721 --> 05:36.501
I promise you this.

05:36.781 --> 05:38.200
Lay down your weapons

05:38.201 --> 05:39.991
and return to the right path,

05:40.521 --> 05:42.021
and you will not be punished.

05:42.811 --> 05:43.951
Otherwise,

05:45.081 --> 05:47.261
the imperial forces will crush you.

05:48.131 --> 05:50.191
Traitors

05:50.641 --> 05:53.261
will never find peace!

05:59.131 --> 06:00.701
Listen, Tengxiang Guards!

06:01.251 --> 06:03.141
Your Commander, Song Han,

06:03.201 --> 06:04.791
has deceived you

06:04.961 --> 06:06.791
and dragged you into treason!

06:07.521 --> 06:09.381
His Majesty has long set up

06:09.691 --> 06:11.021
this trap for you.

06:11.451 --> 06:12.591
You have

06:13.371 --> 06:15.061
no chance of winning!

06:22.201 --> 06:23.751
No one retreats!

06:23.761 --> 06:24.901
Anyone who falls back

06:25.401 --> 06:26.541
will be executed!

06:28.611 --> 06:29.751
Father,

06:30.611 --> 06:32.311
the Crown Prince has been assassinated.

06:33.161 --> 06:34.351
According to protocol,

06:35.161 --> 06:37.381
I should inherit the throne!

06:41.721 --> 06:42.871
Brothers!

06:43.161 --> 06:44.551
We've endured years of suffering

06:45.161 --> 06:46.671
for this day!

06:47.491 --> 06:49.031
Quell the rebels

06:49.281 --> 06:50.941
and protect the nation!

06:51.491 --> 06:53.840
It's now or never.

06:53.841 --> 06:56.370
Quell the rebels and protect the nation!

06:56.371 --> 06:58.690
There's no chance for us to retreat now.

06:58.691 --> 07:00.760
Attack Qianqing Palace
and seize the imperial seal.

07:00.761 --> 07:03.381
Once we succeed, glory and titles await!

07:03.911 --> 07:08.541
Attack!

07:23.251 --> 07:24.391
Meisun,

07:26.611 --> 07:28.021
I won't fail you

07:30.401 --> 07:32.701
this time.

07:48.081 --> 07:49.261
Your Highness, bad news.

07:49.271 --> 07:50.690
The Crown Prince
and the Earl of Yunyang's forces

07:50.691 --> 07:52.160
are attacking from the southern gate.

07:52.161 --> 07:53.320
Wang Xingyi and Official Ji

07:53.321 --> 07:54.991
are also leading large forces here.

08:11.691 --> 08:12.610
Father,

08:12.611 --> 08:14.191
forgive me for my delayed rescue.

08:17.491 --> 08:18.631
On your knees!

08:19.521 --> 08:21.581
Please return to the palace,
Crown Prince!

08:25.011 --> 08:26.581
Please return to the palace.

08:26.591 --> 08:28.541
Dou Zhao wanted me
to give this to Your Highness.

08:28.571 --> 08:29.711
It's urgent.

08:32.241 --> 08:35.031
(The Empress plans to stage a coup
during the Lantern Festival banquet)

08:35.131 --> 08:36.631
(while you're away to the South.)

08:36.851 --> 08:37.991
(After reading this letter,)

08:38.011 --> 08:39.640
(return to the palace immediately
to quell the rebellion)

08:39.641 --> 08:40.981
(and ensure the safety of the nation.)

08:42.281 --> 08:45.210
Your Majesty, I lead 40,000 troops
from the three major camps

08:45.211 --> 08:46.351
to defend the throne.

08:50.401 --> 08:51.701
Lord Qing,

08:52.331 --> 08:53.631
your forces outside the capital

08:54.211 --> 08:56.031
have been completely subdued.

08:56.331 --> 08:57.581
Surrender yourself!

08:57.731 --> 09:00.920
The Duke of Jing, Lord Jihuai,
and Lord Yu'an

09:00.921 --> 09:02.551
have all confessed their crimes.

09:03.281 --> 09:04.421
Your Highness,

09:04.521 --> 09:05.741
the battle is lost.

09:14.131 --> 09:15.311
Everyone, get up!

09:15.681 --> 09:16.821
I said, get up!

09:17.211 --> 09:18.351
Get up!

09:18.371 --> 09:19.511
Get up!

09:19.521 --> 09:21.271
I said, get up!

09:25.441 --> 09:26.581
Ji Yong,

09:27.661 --> 09:29.330
I treated you
with the respect of a mentor

09:29.331 --> 09:30.741
and tolerated everything you did.

09:31.161 --> 09:32.941
Why did you betray me?

09:33.441 --> 09:35.861
I sought fame and power

09:36.061 --> 09:38.040
to cleanse the corrupt court,
eliminate factions,

09:38.041 --> 09:39.701
and save our dynasty from its ailments.

09:40.371 --> 09:42.151
No matter how you treated me,

09:43.251 --> 09:44.370
you were nothing

09:44.371 --> 09:46.791
but the rot that needed
to be cut away first.

09:52.151 --> 09:53.701
The injustice done to the Duke of Ding

09:54.561 --> 09:55.981
and the suffering of the people

09:57.611 --> 09:58.941
must be avenged.

09:59.661 --> 10:02.151
Since when does vengeance have anything
to do with the people?

10:02.401 --> 10:03.551
What a joke!

10:29.681 --> 10:31.151
We did it.

10:33.891 --> 10:35.821
Justice is something
we have to fight for.

10:43.551 --> 10:47.870
(Revere Heaven and Ancestral Wisdom)

10:47.871 --> 10:50.281
Let me go! I said, let me go!

11:00.641 --> 11:03.511
Your Majesty, the Crown Prince has returned
to the palace safely.

11:04.091 --> 11:05.040
Please spare my aunt

11:05.041 --> 11:06.391
from the death penalty.

11:08.441 --> 11:09.941
The Empress's situation

11:11.521 --> 11:13.101
is a matter of state.

11:13.801 --> 11:15.061
It's not up

11:16.331 --> 11:17.941
to you

11:18.441 --> 11:20.191
or me to decide.

11:21.371 --> 11:22.741
Step back.

11:57.761 --> 11:59.741
You fought your way into Qianqing Palace

12:02.211 --> 12:03.861
for this?

12:05.521 --> 12:07.511
I'll give it to you now.

12:08.891 --> 12:10.031
Take it!

12:15.131 --> 12:18.560
Even you know

12:18.561 --> 12:21.701
your merits aren't enough
to bear the weight of the throne.

12:30.161 --> 12:31.631
I can't do it,

12:32.681 --> 12:34.511
but perhaps Mother can.

12:35.801 --> 12:37.311
Once I ascend to the throne,

12:38.211 --> 12:39.821
with her guiding the court,

12:40.131 --> 12:42.101
we may surpass the greatest emperors.

12:42.281 --> 12:43.861
You owe her this!

12:48.211 --> 12:50.341
Your mother has suffered
for half her life.

12:50.761 --> 12:52.330
I always remember that well.

12:52.331 --> 12:54.250
That's why she is the Empress.

12:54.251 --> 12:55.581
She is the Empress.

12:55.891 --> 12:58.581
But she not only tended
to you day and night

12:59.851 --> 13:02.271
but also drafted responses
on your behalf.

13:02.371 --> 13:04.400
When you were gravely ill,

13:04.401 --> 13:06.941
she ruined her eyesight
managing state affairs.

13:07.801 --> 13:10.391
But have you ever considered
her your wife?

13:11.251 --> 13:12.581
You feared her

13:12.951 --> 13:15.581
just as you feared Jiang Meisun.

13:15.851 --> 13:16.991
Youting,

13:17.371 --> 13:19.610
do you know why you failed?

13:19.611 --> 13:21.881
When luck is on your side,
everything works in your favor.

13:23.401 --> 13:25.191
If it's not, even those with power

13:25.971 --> 13:27.151
find themselves powerless.

13:27.491 --> 13:30.341
In Father's heart,

13:30.441 --> 13:32.160
the Duke of Ding and Her Majesty Wan

13:32.161 --> 13:34.941
are worlds apart
in their contributions to the nation.

13:39.521 --> 13:40.661
So,

13:41.131 --> 13:42.311
is all of this...

13:43.921 --> 13:45.941
Is all of this for Jiang Meisun?

13:46.131 --> 13:47.640
Meisun emptied his wealth

13:47.641 --> 13:49.001
for the people,

13:49.011 --> 13:51.671
risked his life for the country,
and formed no allies or factions.

13:52.521 --> 13:54.671
What did you and your mother do?

13:54.891 --> 13:56.271
Who caused

13:56.331 --> 13:57.941
my illness to worsen?

14:06.471 --> 14:08.231
Before you punish me,

14:09.231 --> 14:11.311
I have one question.

14:12.211 --> 14:13.701
When did you

14:15.041 --> 14:17.061
start planning this?

14:20.801 --> 14:22.061
The ruler.

14:24.041 --> 14:25.181
Investigate.

14:25.441 --> 14:27.061
Who used torture?

14:27.491 --> 14:29.671
Who harmed Meisun?

14:30.131 --> 14:33.061
No one should be spared!

14:33.761 --> 14:35.210
And the new era name.

14:35.211 --> 14:39.391
(By the mandate of heaven,
the Emperor declares.)

14:39.561 --> 14:41.671
An auspicious sign has descended.

14:41.681 --> 14:44.391
The era's name changed to Fengming.

14:45.851 --> 14:47.101
Fengming?

14:47.701 --> 14:49.341
How about using this
as the new era name?

14:49.351 --> 14:51.321
Honor past achievements
as guidance to the future.

14:51.331 --> 14:53.081
Clarify doubts
about laws and regulations.

14:53.161 --> 14:54.631
Uphold the legacy of our ancestors

14:54.691 --> 14:56.081
and benefit the lives of the people.

14:56.091 --> 14:57.150
With firm laws,

14:57.151 --> 14:58.941
we restore peace
and fairness to the people.

14:59.091 --> 15:01.850
I wonder if those old officials
in the Ministry of Rites will approve.

15:01.851 --> 15:03.031
Who cares if they approve?

15:03.041 --> 15:04.681
As long as we remember it,
that's enough.

15:06.331 --> 15:08.461
Yes, as long as we remember it.

15:17.281 --> 15:19.191
"Survey the land,

15:20.611 --> 15:22.791
remove unnecessary officials,

15:24.681 --> 15:26.581
curb war,

15:27.891 --> 15:29.821
restrain the powerful,

15:34.851 --> 15:36.861
the ambitions of the past."

15:37.681 --> 15:39.341
Until his death,

15:39.971 --> 15:41.911
I did not achieve these.

15:44.681 --> 15:46.511
Before I die,

15:47.211 --> 15:49.221
I must at least try.

15:49.401 --> 15:51.040
But he was just an unrelated official.

15:51.041 --> 15:52.381
Yet this unrelated official risked

15:53.041 --> 15:56.221
his life to save the nation.

15:56.521 --> 15:58.741
You, my own flesh and blood,

15:58.801 --> 16:01.791
tried to kill me to seize the throne
and harm loyal subjects.

16:04.271 --> 16:05.411
Do you think

16:05.841 --> 16:07.790
people like Mu Chuan
and the Duke of Jing

16:07.791 --> 16:09.631
truly value you

16:09.941 --> 16:12.801
and support Her Majesty Wan
to become the ruler?

16:13.211 --> 16:15.061
They only want to use you

16:15.131 --> 16:17.191
to secure their own endless prosperity!

16:17.211 --> 16:19.191
Those corrupt officials in court

16:19.401 --> 16:21.520
are connected to one another

16:21.521 --> 16:22.741
and even entangled

16:23.341 --> 16:27.221
with the noble clans
and imperial relatives.

16:28.131 --> 16:29.271
When I suppressed

16:29.561 --> 16:31.941
the Futing docks case back then,

16:32.931 --> 16:34.561
I already knew

16:35.441 --> 16:37.341
you weren't the only guilty one.

16:37.851 --> 16:40.191
I wanted
to make you all reveal yourselves

16:40.211 --> 16:43.311
to uproot you in one go.

16:46.371 --> 16:48.271
How ruthless you are.

16:48.891 --> 16:51.671
You're willing
to ruin your wife and son,

16:53.391 --> 16:56.270
and make your uncles and brothers,
meritorious officials for generations

16:56.271 --> 16:57.671
give up their power and be punished.

16:58.441 --> 16:59.440
You staged countless acts

16:59.441 --> 17:01.851
of self-sacrifice for this grand scheme.

17:07.481 --> 17:08.570
Your Majesty,

17:08.571 --> 17:12.391
Lord Qing's treason is undeniable.

17:12.571 --> 17:15.941
Should we summon the Shadow Guards?

17:21.131 --> 17:22.160
Your Majesty,

17:22.161 --> 17:24.071
I believe
I've done something worthy tonight

17:24.681 --> 17:26.221
and boldly request Your Majesty

17:26.441 --> 17:28.071
to issue two imperial decrees.

17:31.051 --> 17:32.191
Do you want me

17:33.161 --> 17:35.351
to execute him?

17:38.941 --> 17:40.671
Those who dare to commit treason

17:40.811 --> 17:43.351
have already dismissed life and death.

17:43.891 --> 17:46.671
His true ambition lies
in power and dominance,

17:46.961 --> 17:49.591
stepping over his father and his kin.

17:50.471 --> 17:51.681
I request Your Majesty

17:51.921 --> 17:54.351
to confine Lord Qing
to the Western Garden for life

17:54.441 --> 17:56.850
and lock him in a three-foot room
without daylight.

17:56.851 --> 17:59.431
Every day, inform him
of Your Majesty and the Crown Prince's

17:59.921 --> 18:01.351
achievements.

18:03.891 --> 18:04.991
No, not that!

18:05.001 --> 18:06.050
Anything but that! Father.

18:06.051 --> 18:07.050
Take him away.

18:07.051 --> 18:09.191
Just kill me! Father!

18:09.331 --> 18:10.871
- Take him away now!
- Please kill me!

18:10.891 --> 18:12.031
Father!

18:12.721 --> 18:14.591
Father, I beg you! Just kill me!

18:14.641 --> 18:15.640
Father!

18:15.641 --> 18:17.301
Father!

18:20.681 --> 18:22.631
Even if Jiang Meisun is here,

18:24.081 --> 18:26.911
he wouldn't dare to convict a prince
on my behalf.

18:27.611 --> 18:29.501
You've got quite the nerve.

18:30.641 --> 18:33.911
So what else do you want?

18:41.051 --> 18:42.000
Song Mo!

18:42.001 --> 18:43.151
What are you doing?

18:46.771 --> 18:50.941
I request to renounce all titles
and military achievements.

18:51.091 --> 18:52.231
I beg Your Majesty

18:53.001 --> 18:55.111
to clear the Duke of Ding

18:55.531 --> 18:56.981
and the Jiang Clan's name.

18:58.891 --> 19:00.920
Of course, I will clear
the Duke of Ding's name.

19:00.921 --> 19:02.061
But you...

19:02.161 --> 19:03.370
What are you doing?

19:03.371 --> 19:05.191
What I ask for isn't for myself

19:05.811 --> 19:07.071
but for justice.

19:10.131 --> 19:11.271
I've lived my life

19:12.331 --> 19:13.981
for loyalty and filial piety.

19:15.051 --> 19:16.941
Then for revenge.

19:17.921 --> 19:19.501
It was not until I met Dou Zhao.

19:20.681 --> 19:22.151
She made me realize

19:23.811 --> 19:25.591
that the hunter must be patient

19:26.331 --> 19:27.471
when he sees prey.

19:28.721 --> 19:30.391
One must be open-minded

19:31.681 --> 19:32.831
when he sees a mountain.

19:34.611 --> 19:36.071
My time is running out.

19:37.201 --> 19:38.911
I want to live for myself,

19:40.441 --> 19:42.351
to see that wide horizon.

19:57.771 --> 19:58.981
Little Song Mo,

20:04.441 --> 20:05.581
take these.

20:25.611 --> 20:27.151
Little Song Mo,

20:30.201 --> 20:32.781
are you really leaving me?

20:44.111 --> 20:48.091
(Peace and Prosperity)

20:59.331 --> 21:00.471
Ansu.

21:17.101 --> 21:18.241
Ansu,

21:19.131 --> 21:20.271
I knew

21:20.571 --> 21:22.261
you would stay by my side.

21:41.441 --> 21:42.581
Ansu,

21:43.481 --> 21:44.911
why did you wait

21:46.721 --> 21:48.301
for me to fall in love with you

21:50.051 --> 21:51.631
before betraying me?

21:53.531 --> 21:54.741
Muyu,

21:57.641 --> 21:59.261
I truly cherished you

22:01.051 --> 22:02.591
once,

22:04.401 --> 22:06.071
that boy who handed me a handkerchief

22:06.601 --> 22:08.541
when I was in distress.

22:08.961 --> 22:10.400
How condescending.

22:10.401 --> 22:11.781
What's wrong with being a merchant?

22:11.961 --> 22:14.021
Earning money with her own skills

22:14.211 --> 22:16.411
is far better than being a lapdog
to the wealthy.

22:17.851 --> 22:19.501
You understood my vulnerability

22:20.161 --> 22:21.981
and knew my struggles.

22:23.131 --> 22:24.391
Here, wipe your sweat.

22:24.611 --> 22:25.960
This is the second time

22:25.961 --> 22:27.431
you've given me a handkerchief.

22:29.891 --> 22:31.191
That boy

22:32.921 --> 22:34.781
who curled up alone,

22:35.611 --> 22:37.021
gazed at the lonely moon

22:38.291 --> 22:39.631
during the festive celebrations.

22:43.051 --> 22:44.781
I once knew you

22:46.401 --> 22:47.640
and admired you.

22:47.641 --> 22:50.191
I'll ask His Majesty
to annul our engagement.

22:50.811 --> 22:51.951
I'm willing to marry you.

22:52.401 --> 22:56.510
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

22:56.511 --> 22:59.400
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

22:59.401 --> 23:00.541
But now,

23:01.611 --> 23:03.221
you want me dead.

23:04.441 --> 23:06.351
Dying by my hand

23:07.291 --> 23:08.701
will bring you some peace.

23:09.771 --> 23:10.950
I've hated you.

23:10.951 --> 23:13.901
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

23:14.611 --> 23:16.831
But I also don't want others
to defile you.

23:18.381 --> 23:22.270
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

23:22.271 --> 23:25.790
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

23:25.791 --> 23:30.230
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

23:30.231 --> 23:33.961
♪Having you is a blessing♪

23:34.331 --> 23:35.330
Ansu...

23:35.331 --> 23:36.781
Ansu. Ansu.

23:38.721 --> 23:41.541
If I could change my ways,

23:43.531 --> 23:45.111
would you forgive me?

23:45.631 --> 23:49.871
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

23:49.991 --> 23:53.191
♪Always together, looking back♪

23:53.561 --> 24:00.841
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

24:16.791 --> 24:21.811
(Xuanyue Palace)

24:28.531 --> 24:30.071
You've already guessed the whole thing

24:31.241 --> 24:33.151
about the Silverhouse case.

24:33.641 --> 24:35.151
Rather than guess,

24:35.161 --> 24:36.351
I would say it was a gamble.

24:36.921 --> 24:38.071
If I lost,

24:38.401 --> 24:40.021
I'd just die a little faster.

24:40.811 --> 24:43.431
If you get what you want and gain power,

24:44.611 --> 24:46.261
you won't let me live long either.

24:55.791 --> 24:57.781
Every time I see you,

24:58.401 --> 25:00.941
I see myself before entering the palace.

25:01.161 --> 25:02.301
No,

25:02.531 --> 25:03.781
we're not the same.

25:04.401 --> 25:06.391
I trust the person

25:06.861 --> 25:08.151
I love in this life.

25:16.851 --> 25:17.991
Your Majesty,

25:18.891 --> 25:20.871
His Majesty summons you.

25:22.611 --> 25:24.111
Given everything that's happened,

25:25.131 --> 25:28.591
I feel disgusted just thinking
about seeing him.

25:29.201 --> 25:30.431
His Majesty said,

25:30.721 --> 25:33.301
if you can't face him,

25:33.531 --> 25:36.191
you are to move to Qianxi

25:36.811 --> 25:38.090
and never step foot

25:38.091 --> 25:41.221
outside again.

25:46.331 --> 25:47.671
He's not deposing me?

25:48.051 --> 25:50.261
His Majesty is merciful.

25:59.771 --> 26:02.151
But I don't want to continue
this charade any longer

26:04.001 --> 26:05.541
or

26:06.091 --> 26:08.631
this fake marriage.

26:09.961 --> 26:12.391
In life or death,

26:13.161 --> 26:15.301
I hope to never see him again.

26:17.891 --> 26:18.960
Tell him

26:18.961 --> 26:20.701
I willingly renounce my title as Empress

26:21.091 --> 26:22.641
and request to be demoted to a commoner.

26:22.741 --> 26:24.151
I ask for death.

26:35.331 --> 26:36.471
Dou Zhao,

26:44.441 --> 26:45.581
farewell.

27:13.131 --> 27:15.791
♪The glitter of the beautiful terrace
is just a fleeting splendor♪

27:16.381 --> 27:19.031
♪The army halts at your command♪

27:19.761 --> 27:21.100
♪Bending down for a single kiss♪

27:21.101 --> 27:23.400
♪Forsaking words of farewell♪

27:23.401 --> 27:24.541
Yantang.

27:26.261 --> 27:28.921
♪The golden fiery steed rides
across the vast horizon♪

27:29.561 --> 27:32.591
♪In this life, oh♪

27:32.831 --> 27:38.011
♪What is there to envy without you?♪

27:38.541 --> 27:41.020
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

27:41.021 --> 27:45.360
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

27:45.361 --> 27:52.171
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms
bloom in a single night for you♪

27:52.231 --> 27:55.331
♪The splendor of the world
is but fleeting sorrow♪

27:55.381 --> 27:58.661
♪Should the flames of war arise♪

27:58.701 --> 28:01.480
♪I shall hold your hand♪

28:01.481 --> 28:03.871
Don't let me wait for you
outside the palace walls anymore.

28:04.641 --> 28:07.191
I don't want to see
these cold walls again.

28:09.851 --> 28:11.450
You no longer need to worry about me.

28:11.451 --> 28:14.041
♪From now on,
all the vast wonders of the world♪

28:14.201 --> 28:15.501
I will live.

28:17.721 --> 28:19.461
Did His Majesty give you the antidote?

28:21.911 --> 28:24.971
♪Is no match for your beauty♪

28:25.141 --> 28:27.750
♪Why ascend to high towers again?♪

28:27.751 --> 28:32.251
(Qianqing Palace)

28:35.591 --> 28:41.091
(Revere Heaven and Ancestral Wisdom)

28:52.371 --> 28:53.511
Your Majesty,

28:54.611 --> 28:57.351
why did you give the only snow lingzhi

28:57.371 --> 28:58.871
to Song Mo?

28:59.291 --> 29:03.301
That is your life-saving lingzhi.

29:04.531 --> 29:08.431
The snow lingzhi has indeed been extinct
for centuries.

29:08.681 --> 29:10.391
Only the founding emperor

29:10.771 --> 29:13.351
once gifted it to the Wanfo Temple.

29:13.641 --> 29:15.351
I risked leaving the palace

29:15.531 --> 29:16.911
for this.

29:17.401 --> 29:18.850
While we have the snow lingzhi,

29:18.851 --> 29:21.911
the poison of hatred is a human toxin.

29:22.331 --> 29:25.200
Formulating an antidote requires
great care

29:25.201 --> 29:27.021
and cannot be done overnight.

29:34.771 --> 29:37.221
I am already at the end of my life.

29:37.811 --> 29:39.221
I don't need it anymore.

29:41.531 --> 29:42.831
I gave it to Yantang,

29:42.851 --> 29:45.151
so he could protect Yousheng forever.

29:49.641 --> 29:51.541
You're not young anymore.

29:51.721 --> 29:53.391
Yet you still act like a child.

29:55.091 --> 29:56.160
I can't even remember

29:56.161 --> 29:58.631
the last time you cried.

30:01.851 --> 30:04.261
That was more than fifty years ago.

30:08.131 --> 30:09.301
Yes,

30:12.161 --> 30:13.871
it was more than fifty years ago.

30:20.161 --> 30:21.981
I want to walk alone for a while.

30:28.951 --> 30:32.491
(Qianqing Palace)

30:33.531 --> 30:35.291
(The way of heaven is not distant.)

30:36.411 --> 30:38.301
(The admonition is not false.)

30:38.891 --> 30:40.781
(The people's wrongdoings rest)

30:41.161 --> 30:42.941
(with me alone.)

30:44.051 --> 30:46.391
(Now I deeply regret my actions.)

30:47.131 --> 30:51.021
(How can I allow slander to take root,)

30:51.331 --> 30:55.431
(causing loyal ministers to be wronged
and the Jiang Clan unjustly exiled?)

30:55.851 --> 30:59.461
(The divine retribution has come,
and I failed to awaken in time.)

30:59.961 --> 31:01.631
(The people's resentment has risen,)

31:02.241 --> 31:04.351
(yet I was blind to it.)

31:06.181 --> 31:07.961
(The Emperor issued
a self-punishing edict)

31:08.011 --> 31:10.391
(to clear the names
of the Duke of Ding and the Jiang Clan.)

31:10.931 --> 31:13.431
(Lord Qing's supporters
were all executed for treason.)

31:13.441 --> 31:15.770
(The following year,
the Crown Prince ascended the throne,)

31:15.771 --> 31:17.101
(granting a general amnesty.)

31:17.671 --> 31:19.721
(Ji Yong was promoted
to the Minister of Personnel.)

31:19.731 --> 31:22.111
(He's the first Chief Grand Secretary
of the new dynasty.)

31:22.511 --> 31:25.091
(Wu Shan is the Assistant Minister
of the Ministry of Works now.)

31:25.571 --> 31:27.130
(The new dynasty implemented reforms,)

31:27.131 --> 31:29.381
(emphasizing agriculture,
returning land to the people,)

31:29.391 --> 31:30.981
(and rigorously scrutinizing
government officials.)

31:30.991 --> 31:33.501
(The political and societal structure
has been transformed.)

31:40.351 --> 31:43.691
(Tiancang Festival, Five Years Later)

31:44.271 --> 31:47.171
(Abundance)

31:54.051 --> 31:55.191
Fetch the beans.

32:00.571 --> 32:01.711
Here you go.

32:02.091 --> 32:03.831
Let me grab some.

32:04.091 --> 32:05.741
A bountiful harvest!

32:06.571 --> 32:08.541
Granaries overflowing with harvest.

32:20.641 --> 32:21.911
It's hung quite high this time.

32:23.051 --> 32:24.301
Yours is even higher!

32:25.891 --> 32:27.031
Not bad.

32:33.201 --> 32:36.021
Now that the world is settled,

32:37.201 --> 32:39.911
and the court is reformed
with many challenges ahead,

32:40.401 --> 32:42.221
why are you retiring?

32:42.351 --> 32:44.530
Once, I believed
that ordinary physicians heal diseases

32:44.531 --> 32:46.081
while great physicians heal the nation.

32:46.571 --> 32:48.941
Becoming the Chief Grand Secretary
was my life's ambition.

32:49.721 --> 32:51.701
Now that I've achieved it,

32:52.131 --> 32:53.981
I find it rather boring.

32:54.501 --> 32:56.261
A life of quiet cultivation
suits me better.

32:56.721 --> 32:58.301
Letting go of obsessions

32:58.891 --> 33:00.501
brings true freedom.

33:01.001 --> 33:03.461
Now that your emotions
are fully engaged,

33:04.001 --> 33:07.501
your thoughts are tied
to just one person.

33:10.531 --> 33:11.981
All things are empty,

33:12.401 --> 33:13.941
but cause and effect are real.

33:14.371 --> 33:17.911
These worldly affairs
are like fleeting clouds.

33:18.161 --> 33:21.351
I hope you can understand
the cause and effect in the world,

33:22.131 --> 33:24.541
and your worries will disappear.

33:40.531 --> 33:42.021
Father! Mother!

33:42.201 --> 33:44.610
Wake up, Father! Play with me, Mother!

33:44.611 --> 33:45.981
Your daughter is calling you.

33:47.721 --> 33:50.831
Yesterday, she climbed trees
and went to catch some fish.

33:51.531 --> 33:53.351
She's only slept a few hours.

33:57.851 --> 33:59.431
Father! Mother!

34:01.001 --> 34:03.050
Father. Mother.

34:03.051 --> 34:04.720
Get up and play with me.

34:04.721 --> 34:05.680
Father! Mother!

34:05.681 --> 34:07.720
- Get up and play with me.
- All right, I'm up.

34:07.721 --> 34:09.701
Father. Mother.

34:13.731 --> 34:15.671
Go play in the courtyard for a while.

34:15.731 --> 34:17.031
I'll be right there.

34:18.001 --> 34:19.960
Father and Mother, hurry up.

34:19.961 --> 34:20.850
Go on.

34:20.851 --> 34:22.151
Don't run too fast.

34:25.401 --> 34:26.951
Raising a child

34:27.731 --> 34:29.701
is harder than doing business.

34:30.101 --> 34:31.841
It's more exhausting
than fighting a battle.

34:31.851 --> 34:33.701
We used to say

34:33.731 --> 34:35.551
that once the world was at peace,

34:35.601 --> 34:37.551
we would go and travel together.

34:38.171 --> 34:39.381
But now,

34:39.891 --> 34:41.290
one day,

34:41.291 --> 34:42.600
the walls fall,

34:42.601 --> 34:43.850
and the garden explodes next.

34:43.851 --> 34:45.511
Year after year,
there's always something.

34:46.081 --> 34:49.330
But Grandmother, she's been
to so many places these past years.

34:49.331 --> 34:50.991
She'll be home soon.

34:52.001 --> 34:53.141
This time,

34:53.171 --> 34:54.551
we can definitely go.

34:55.081 --> 34:56.170
How so?

34:56.171 --> 34:57.120
Have you forgotten?

34:57.121 --> 34:58.921
Lianjun is going to school soon.

34:59.251 --> 35:00.391
How can I forget that?

35:00.811 --> 35:01.951
Make the arrangements, then.

35:02.431 --> 35:03.571
Let's go.

35:05.371 --> 35:08.031
Mr. Feng comes from a scholarly family

35:08.171 --> 35:10.261
and is ranked second in the palace exam.

35:11.251 --> 35:12.730
How could a man from a poor family

35:12.731 --> 35:15.301
be worthy of our Princess Anyu?

35:16.801 --> 35:19.250
I came to evaluate the officials
of the Ministry of Revenue,

35:19.251 --> 35:20.741
not to choose a husband.

35:21.371 --> 35:23.421
You'll find one after some picking.

35:24.531 --> 35:27.250
The eldest son of Taiyuan Bank,
Young Master Zhang.

35:27.251 --> 35:29.250
Third Master Wan
of Dongting Chamber of Commerce.

35:29.251 --> 35:31.960
They truly love you.

35:31.961 --> 35:33.690
So what if they have wealth?

35:33.691 --> 35:37.440
Together, those three can't compare
to Princess Anyu's wealth

35:37.441 --> 35:38.861
that can't be kept track.

35:39.251 --> 35:41.831
The son of Marquis Dongping, Lord Han.

35:41.841 --> 35:43.521
A man of both literary
and martial skills.

35:43.551 --> 35:47.511
This is a match worthy of the princess.

35:47.551 --> 35:49.520
- Wealth still matters.
- Mr. Feng is the best.

35:49.521 --> 35:50.520
Lord Han is the best.

35:50.521 --> 35:51.701
Ladies,

35:51.731 --> 35:53.650
where are you your manners

35:53.651 --> 35:55.031
for bickering like this?

35:57.561 --> 36:00.000
Gentlemen, as for this item in the drawing,

36:00.001 --> 36:01.440
it can be used both as a staple food

36:01.441 --> 36:03.621
and to make sugar, brew wine,
or grind flour.

36:03.631 --> 36:05.431
It can be grown
in both the north and south.

36:05.441 --> 36:06.690
Whoever can calculate

36:06.691 --> 36:08.270
the cost and profit

36:08.271 --> 36:10.031
of growing and selling it for one year,

36:10.371 --> 36:11.551
I'll choose him.

36:19.251 --> 36:22.261
They don't work with their hands
and have no knowledge of farming.

36:23.251 --> 36:25.701
No wonder people say
scholars are useless.

36:26.251 --> 36:28.151
You're even more useful by my side.

36:28.251 --> 36:29.631
Dismiss them all.

36:30.401 --> 36:31.440
Please don't.

36:31.441 --> 36:33.191
You must choose a prince consort.

36:33.291 --> 36:35.111
That's the Empress's order.

36:41.561 --> 36:43.151
These wheat grains are really big.

36:44.731 --> 36:46.170
No matter what Su brings back,

36:46.171 --> 36:47.920
it can't beat me, a great cook.

36:47.921 --> 36:49.341
Hurry up and remove the grains.

36:49.381 --> 36:50.551
I want to stir-fry some.

36:50.921 --> 36:53.671
Can lotus root and wheat

36:53.921 --> 36:54.960
really go together?

36:54.961 --> 36:56.890
Sometimes things
that don't seem to go together

36:56.891 --> 36:58.821
end up having an unexpected flavor
when combined.

36:58.831 --> 37:00.381
Don't you understand this principle?

37:03.001 --> 37:04.141
Yes,

37:05.001 --> 37:06.151
just like us.

37:07.891 --> 37:09.191
What are you talking about?

37:10.731 --> 37:11.951
Nothing.

37:12.561 --> 37:13.991
Everything you say is right, my dear.

37:14.251 --> 37:15.551
Stop flattering me.

37:15.861 --> 37:17.781
Hurry up. Grandmother will be here soon.

37:19.851 --> 37:21.120
You've been traveling

37:21.121 --> 37:22.551
for a full three months.

37:23.171 --> 37:24.890
It's unfilial of me

37:24.891 --> 37:26.031
not to accompany you.

37:26.921 --> 37:29.811
Next time you go on a trip,

37:30.001 --> 37:32.381
I'll join you during my leave.
Is that all right?

37:33.601 --> 37:34.960
My body

37:34.961 --> 37:36.671
is still strong.

37:37.691 --> 37:39.991
Madam Tuo takes good care of me.

37:40.121 --> 37:41.701
So you don't have to worry.

37:42.231 --> 37:44.011
You've been promoted

37:44.151 --> 37:47.171
and are helping
His Majesty compile historical records.

37:47.831 --> 37:49.710
How do you have any free time?

37:49.711 --> 37:51.201
Filial piety is paramount.

37:51.231 --> 37:53.281
There's always time to accompany you.

37:53.541 --> 37:54.721
I just hope

37:55.061 --> 37:56.971
you won't find me a nuisance.

37:58.671 --> 38:00.091
I've heard recently

38:00.191 --> 38:04.281
that quite a few court officials
have tried matchmaking for you.

38:04.381 --> 38:06.131
But you turned them all down.

38:07.381 --> 38:09.131
At my age,

38:09.381 --> 38:11.241
can we leave this topic alone?

38:12.151 --> 38:15.281
Lately,
I've been dreaming of Guqiu often.

38:15.901 --> 38:17.401
The magnolia tree at the old house

38:17.421 --> 38:19.171
finally bloomed this year.

38:19.501 --> 38:21.111
I brewed some magnolia wine.

38:22.231 --> 38:23.441
If she were still here,

38:24.231 --> 38:25.611
she would have loved it.

38:32.341 --> 38:33.580
Ms. Longevity and I made a deal

38:33.581 --> 38:35.321
to keep the matchmaking a secret.

38:35.581 --> 38:37.011
How did you find out?

38:37.021 --> 38:39.331
Great Grandmother! Grandfather!

38:40.721 --> 38:42.681
- My dear great-granddaughter.
- Sweetie.

38:42.871 --> 38:45.190
Great Grandmother knows everything.

38:45.191 --> 38:47.020
But you don't.

38:47.021 --> 38:49.761
Great Grandmother has spies
in the household.

38:50.941 --> 38:52.531
Let me carry her instead.

38:52.581 --> 38:53.500
Old Madam,

38:53.501 --> 38:56.681
didn't you buy gifts for Little Miss?

38:57.061 --> 38:58.321
Ah, yes.

38:58.941 --> 39:00.630
My dear great-granddaughter,

39:00.631 --> 39:02.761
shall we go and take a look at them?

39:03.501 --> 39:05.771
Mother, what spy?

39:05.871 --> 39:08.591
I... I bought a lot of local produce.

39:10.021 --> 39:13.100
This famous official is known
for his stern character

39:13.101 --> 39:15.500
and frugal lifestyle.

39:15.501 --> 39:19.670
The court granted him a carriage
for his convenience to go to court.

39:19.671 --> 39:22.721
His son, however,
used it to go to school.

39:22.981 --> 39:25.011
Yang Zhen stopped the carriage

39:25.711 --> 39:30.420
and scolded his son
for using the court's carriage.

39:30.421 --> 39:32.670
If he's too lazy to walk to school now,

39:32.671 --> 39:35.261
how will he endure hardships
as an official?

39:37.231 --> 39:38.371
Exactly.

39:38.871 --> 39:40.011
Yes, indeed.

39:40.231 --> 39:42.801
Reading thousands of books

39:43.101 --> 39:45.790
is not as good
as traveling thousands of miles.

39:45.791 --> 39:47.281
Serving as an official

39:47.301 --> 39:49.071
is about seeking the welfare
of the people.

39:51.791 --> 39:52.931
Jiang Shu,

39:54.501 --> 39:56.810
when did Lianjun leave?

39:56.811 --> 39:58.230
(Jiang Shu, son of Duke of Ding)
She slipped away

39:58.231 --> 40:00.230
when you started talking

40:00.231 --> 40:01.841
about reading thousands of books.

40:05.831 --> 40:07.401
Just like her mother.

40:21.151 --> 40:22.401
A place full of flowers,

40:22.671 --> 40:23.811
cups brimming with wine,

40:24.711 --> 40:26.881
and freedom in the waves of a vast lake.

40:27.711 --> 40:29.241
The scenery, along the way,

40:29.351 --> 40:30.681
is beautiful,

40:31.231 --> 40:32.721
just as you wish.

40:33.061 --> 40:33.930
And the wine?

40:33.931 --> 40:37.301
♪Like ink drops fading into my heart♪

40:38.461 --> 40:39.681
The smell of magnolia.

40:39.981 --> 40:41.201
Where did you get this?

40:42.351 --> 40:44.971
Father-in-law's homemade brew.

40:46.231 --> 40:47.600
I secretly took it.

40:47.601 --> 40:49.791
♪Never tired after a hundred battles♪

40:50.901 --> 40:53.401
Now that justice has been served

40:54.151 --> 40:56.190
and we've finally fulfilled our dream
of traveling.

40:56.191 --> 40:57.331
Ms. Longevity,

40:57.541 --> 41:00.080
how about we make another wish?

41:00.081 --> 41:00.970
Sure.

41:00.971 --> 41:04.741
♪Together with you, wing to wing,
our shadows flying♪

41:05.231 --> 41:07.700
May our love endure
and stay united for a lifetime.

41:07.701 --> 41:09.480
♪Morning and night, with clear skies♪

41:09.481 --> 41:11.661
♪Clear wind and bright moon,
we wait for them♪

41:11.861 --> 41:14.480
♪Waiting for the fog to disperse
and the clouds to clear♪

41:14.481 --> 41:16.320
♪Tears that fall,
half a lifetime of tears♪

41:16.321 --> 41:20.721
♪Melted by your kiss,
melted by your kiss♪

41:21.261 --> 41:23.450
♪In this life, I wish to be
like Mandarin ducks in the water♪

41:23.451 --> 41:25.421
♪The green shore
is more beautiful than the sky♪

41:25.601 --> 41:28.250
♪The splendor doesn't intoxicate
the eyes♪

41:28.251 --> 41:29.980
♪Spring returns,
the swaying green lotus♪

41:29.981 --> 41:35.000
♪The mountains are distant, what do I have to envy?♪
♪Even so, I don't envy them♪

41:35.001 --> 41:37.210
♪In this life,
I wish to keep my promise to you♪

41:37.211 --> 41:39.390
♪Unchanged even to old age♪

41:39.391 --> 41:42.000
♪I will definitely fulfill the promise
without fail♪

41:42.001 --> 41:48.091
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

41:57.081 --> 42:00.150
♪I want to hide like the moon♪

42:00.151 --> 42:03.711
♪Like a butterfly drawn to flowers♪

42:03.941 --> 42:10.010
♪Like ink drops fading into my heart
that turns to longing♪

42:10.011 --> 42:13.750
♪Like the sun waiting
for the flying wild geese♪

42:13.751 --> 42:17.141
♪The sound of weapons chasing
the long whip♪

42:17.671 --> 42:23.521
♪Never tired after a hundred battles,
because of you♪

42:24.001 --> 42:25.920
♪Morning and night, we meet again♪

42:25.921 --> 42:27.500
♪Walking slowly towards the distance♪

42:27.501 --> 42:30.870
♪Like leaves tangled in the wind,
tightly intertwined♪

42:30.871 --> 42:32.980
♪Together with you, wing to wing♪

42:32.981 --> 42:37.760
♪Our shadows flying,
dwelling together year after year♪

42:37.761 --> 42:39.520
♪Morning and night, with clear skies♪

42:39.521 --> 42:41.761
♪Clear wind and bright moon,
we wait for them♪

42:41.871 --> 42:44.470
♪Waiting for the fog to disperse
and the clouds to clear♪

42:44.471 --> 42:46.390
♪Tears that fall,
half a lifetime of tears♪

42:46.391 --> 42:50.531
♪Melted by your kiss,
melted by your kiss♪

42:51.251 --> 42:53.460
♪In this life, I wish to be
like Mandarin ducks in the water♪

42:53.461 --> 42:55.691
♪The green shore is more beautiful
than the sky♪

42:55.701 --> 42:58.280
♪The splendor doesn't intoxicate
the eyes♪

