43:53.381 --> 43:54.611
So, what do you think?

43:55.021 --> 43:56.451
It's not that great.

43:56.461 --> 43:58.940
My mother has a book just like this.

43:58.941 --> 44:00.321
I'm not impressed.

44:01.791 --> 44:03.460
My mother already told me

44:03.461 --> 44:04.900
the stories in her book.

44:04.901 --> 44:07.651
It's nothing like
what you wrote in yours.

44:09.061 --> 44:10.761
That's not quite right.

44:10.871 --> 44:12.020
The stories in this book

44:12.021 --> 44:13.841
might have happened once.

44:14.461 --> 44:17.721
Maybe somewhere in this world,

44:18.151 --> 44:20.651
someone extraordinary changed
the fate of those in the book.

44:21.421 --> 44:24.011
They changed not only the people
who were in the book

44:24.351 --> 44:26.491
but also those who were never mentioned.

44:26.501 --> 44:27.971
On that land,

44:27.981 --> 44:30.350
so many lives were touched

44:30.351 --> 44:33.131
and had their fate changed,

44:33.671 --> 44:34.540
That's why

44:34.541 --> 44:37.651
the stories in this book
aren't the same.

44:38.751 --> 44:39.670
I don't get it.

44:39.671 --> 44:41.420
I think you're a swindler.

44:41.421 --> 44:42.310
I'm leaving now.

44:42.311 --> 44:43.940
Don't ever lie to children again.

44:43.941 --> 44:45.971
I'll tell my mother if you do.

44:46.271 --> 44:48.020
Wait, little girl.

44:48.021 --> 44:50.491
If you don't like that book,

44:50.791 --> 44:53.980
other than "Blossom,"

44:53.981 --> 44:57.131
("Blossom" Series)
I have the sequels of "Blossom."

44:57.231 --> 45:00.190
Every sequel has a different ending.

45:00.191 --> 45:03.171
Aren't you curious
about the ending of other sequels?
